# Cloud Build upload allowlist (gitignore syntax; last match wins).
#
# The agent-sniper image (deploy/sniper/cloudbuild.yaml) builds from the REPO
# ROOT and its Dockerfile copies the root package manifests, api/, and the
# agent-payments-sdk/ workspace — NOT just workers/. The previous allowlist
# uploaded only workers/, so the sniper Cloud Build context was missing those
# paths and `COPY package.json` / `COPY api` failed. Re-include exactly what the
# worker images need, and keep multi-GB node_modules + .git out of the upload.
/*
!/workers/
!/api/
!/src/
!/agent-payments-sdk/
!/package.json
!/package-lock.json
!/.npmrc
!/.gcloudignore
# Re-exclude heavy/derived paths even inside the re-included directories.
**/node_modules/
.git/
